pohoda-zabbix (0.2.0) trixie; urgency=low

  * Add --period option to pohoda-zabbix-digest (month, year, YYYY)
  * Add PohodaDataProvider with dateTill fix and isOnline connectivity check
  * Switch all dependencies to Packagist (no local path repositories)
  * Per-period cache files (digest_cache_YYYY-MM-DD_YYYY-MM-DD.json)
  * Fix debtors and outcoming_invoices Zabbix metrics (upstream digest-modules)

